The paper discusses the integration of UAVs in cellular networks, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), robotics (cs.RO), cyber-physical security (cs.CR), control systems (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
